+--------------------------------------+--------------------+--------------------+------------+
| #!/[0-9a-z]{8}-[0-9a-z]{4}-[0-9a-z]{4}-[0-9a-z]{4}-[0-9a-z]{12}/!# | advanced_assistant | openai:gpt-4o      | %{NUMBER} |
| #!/[0-9a-z]{8}-[0-9a-z]{4}-[0-9a-z]{4}-[0-9a-z]{4}-[0-9a-z]{12}/!# | test_assistant     | openai:gpt-4o-mini | %{NUMBER} |
+--------------------------------------+--------------------+--------------------+------------+
